{"tid":2358493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★私樓又輸！民政處 會主動派員到私樓進行家訪，查核居民是否已有檢測紀錄","createTime":"2021-01-08T07:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T06:22:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3df029b3d27c14fbd9e9bab27600e26cb2691413","tid":2358493,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:28:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">強制檢測私樓住戶須向民政處交資料</span><br />\n<br />\n在私人大廈方面，由於民政事務總署無法聯絡沒有到流動採樣站接受檢測的住戶單位的居民，署方需要主動接觸居民，請他們提交在其他途徑已作出檢測的資料。民政處會透過業主立案法團和大廈的物業管理公司提供協助，向大廈住客發出通告及在大堂張貼通告，提醒大廈的住客聯絡民政處提交資料。民政處亦已主動<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>派員到一些大廈進行家訪</strong></span>，以查核居民是否已有檢測紀錄。署方希望首先核實及以協助和勸諭的形式，盡快落實強制檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/571663/%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2%E8%88%87%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B-%E6%88%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%8F%8A%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%98%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E6%8F%AA%E9%81%95%E5%BC%B7%E6%AA%A2%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F571663%2F%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%2598%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E6%258F%25AA%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2588%25B6&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=6f438778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/571663/%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2%E8%88%87%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B-%E6%88%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%8F%8A%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%98%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E6%8F%AA%E9%81%95%E5%BC%B7%E6%AA%A2%E5%85%AC%E5%91%8A%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B6</a>"},{"pid":"4d80c9e681741d8645f1530f56ef7e579a9aa995","tid":235849